WEBVTT

00:07:27.070 --> 00:07:31.459
it drives a pin into the ground.

00:07:31.483 --> 00:07:33.999
(Laughter)

00:07:34.023 --> 00:07:35.188
Audience member: Wow!

00:07:35.212 --> 00:07:37.334
The nose is fixed,
the whole animal is fixed.

00:07:37.358 --> 00:07:41.345
The wind may turn, but the animal
will always turn its nose into the wind.

00:07:44.308 --> 00:07:49.809
Now, another couple of years, and these
animals will survive on their own.

00:07:50.277 --> 00:07:51.833
I still have to help them a lot.

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:54.507
Thank you very much, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:54.531 --> 00:07:56.024
(Applause)